  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Add the <strong>ground turmeric</strong>,<strong> smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> half </strong>the<strong> curry powder</strong>,<strong> half</strong> the<strong> Greek-style yogurt </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>to a large bowl and stir it all together – this is your <strong>tandoori marinade</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to the<strong> tandoori marinade </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>marinated chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
