    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> potato cubes </strong>to the other side of the tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>remaining curry powder</strong> over the<strong> potato cubes</strong>, season with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> – these are your<strong> spiced roast potatoes</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 18-20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
